.demo-description
  %p    
    Another great feature which is requested many times from the community - custom creation of 
    editable elements. This is done with the following settings in colModel - 
    %code
      edittype:'custom' 
    and two functions - one to create the element and another to get the value from it.
  %p
    In this example click on a row to edit it and see what is happens when you perform saving
    in the column 
    %i
      Note.
/ End demo-description
